name: Goospace
description:
Goospace is a side-scroller jump game.

Explore the universe.
Jump, black holes, various satellites and planets and stars.
you can explore a lot of experiences in this game.

Collect birds.
This game has various birds with their unique abilities.

Collect achievements.
This game has various achievements.

Try speedrun
This game encourages the speedrun and setting up high-scores.
try to get best scores.
